quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  88,22,"Ìwọ kì í ṣe ajẹni-nípá lórí wọn"
  88,23,"àfi ẹni tí ó bá pẹ̀yìndà (sí òdodo), tí ó sì ṣàì gbàgbọ́."
  88,24,"Allāhu sì máa jẹ ẹ́ níyà tó tóbi jùlọ."
  89,19,"Ẹ tún ń jẹ ogún ní ìjẹkújẹ."
  89,20,"Àti pé ẹ nífẹ̀ẹ́ sí dúkìá ní ìfẹ́ púpọ̀."
  89,21,"Rárá, (kò yẹ kó rí bẹ́ẹ̀). Nígbà tí wọ́n bá mi ilẹ̀ tìtì ní mímì tìtì (tó rún wómúwómú, tí kò sí kòtò, tí kò sí gelemọ),"
  90,13,"(Òhun ni) títú ẹrú sílẹ̀ lóko ẹrú."
  90,14,"Tàbí fífún ènìyàn ní oúnjẹ ní ọjọ́ ebi."
  90,15,"(Ẹ lè fún) ọmọ-òrukàn nínú ẹbí,"
  91,10,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá fi (ìwà ẹ̀ṣẹ̀) ba ẹ̀mí (ara) rẹ̀ jẹ́, ó mà ti pàdánù."
  91,11,"Ìjọ Thamūd pe òdodo ní irọ́ nípa ìtayọ ẹnu-ààlà wọn."
  91,12,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ẹni tí orí rẹ̀ burú jùlọ nínú wọn sáré dìde (láti gún ràkúnmí pa)."
  92,7,"A sì máa ṣe iṣẹ́ rere ní ìrọ̀rùn fún un."
  92,8,"Ní ti ẹni tí ó bá yahun, tí ó sì rí ara rẹ̀ lẹ́ni tó rọrọ̀ tayọ ẹ̀san ọ̀run,"
  92,9,"(tí) ó tún pe ẹ̀san rere (Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra) ní irọ́,"
  93,4,"Dájúdájú ọ̀run lóore fún ọ ju ayé."
  93,5,"Dájúdájú láìpẹ́ Olúwa rẹ máa fún ọ ní (oore púpọ̀ ní ọ̀run). Nítorí náà, o sì máa yọ́nú sí i."
  93,6,"Ṣé (Allāhu) kò rí ọ ní ọmọ-òrukàn ni? Ó sì fún ọ ní ibùgbé."
  94,1,"Ṣé A kò ṣípayá igbá-àyà rẹ fún ọ bí?"
  94,2,"A sì gbé ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ rẹ kúrò lọ́rùn rẹ,"
  94,3,"èyí tí ó wọ̀ ọ́ lọ́rùn.1 {1}",footnotes:1:Bí ó tilẹ̀ jẹ́ pé Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - kò ṣẹbọ rí ṣíwájú kí ó tó di Òjíṣẹ́ Allāhu, ọ̀kan nínú ohun tí ó máa ń kọ Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - lóminú, tí ó sì máa ń bà á nínú jẹ́ ni àìdá ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo mọ̀ àti àìní ìlànà ìjọ́sìn kan lọ́wọ́ ṣíwájú ogójì ọdún tí ó kọ́kọ́ lò.